Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:08.12,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know! I can't believe it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:10.58,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The map has never called me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:14.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's not why she looks… like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Actually, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:20.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, it's that, and the fact that you've been called to the Royal Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:23.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean, what in Equestria could be going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:25.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:27.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The map just called you for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:28.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:29.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Though maybe it's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:33.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Because it's never called just one of us before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.58,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I also wasn't nervous before, but now…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, for all we know it's something small.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:45.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Like maybe the cooks are fighting over who has the best butternut squash soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:48.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or the royal hairdressers are fighting over a comb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:51.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Or, you know, maybe the royal sisters aren't seeing eye to eye on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:52.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:55.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Luna and Celestia would never fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:57.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:05.06,Celestia,,0,0,0,,So, the map sent you to solve a friendship problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:06.46,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yes, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:08.48,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Well, there's nothing wrong here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:09.92,Celestia,,0,0,0,,right, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:13.74,Luna,,0,0,0,,No. Everything is perfect as usual, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:09.37,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:11.65,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Is that you? How are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not, I'm still home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:16.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's an easy spell, I'll show you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Anyway, enough about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'd to check on you, but not in a meddling kind of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:20.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,In a friendly how's-it-going kind of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.81,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Not great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:27.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I think the problem might be between Celestia and Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:29.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh no, that's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:32.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean… what makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:37.99,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You know how someponies say nothing's wrong, but you can tell something's definitely wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:44.25,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's basically what the Princesses did when I said there was a friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Only they did it more… regally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I wish I could help you, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Both for map reasons and because I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is big! Like, really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I'm here if you ever need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or to listen a music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Comforting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.51,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for breakfast, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.51,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you cook it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Of course, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.19,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I really enjoy doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:20.59,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It's a small way to say "I care".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.37,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Good morning, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:26.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.25,Luna,,0,0,0,,Too tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.85,Luna,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.45,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Wow. Last night must've been really hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:40.87,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, but… she is like this every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:50.31,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So, I think Luna may be hurting her sister's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.11,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Without even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Poor Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:56.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's so sweet that she makes her sister pancakes every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,She's your mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.37,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I think you might be biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.57,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Nothing… yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I have to get all the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.53,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Luna if I can spend some time with her this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.99,Guard,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna's waiting for you, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.29,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Wow, Princess Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You do this every night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:30.67,Luna,,0,0,0,,Lavenders calming scent is known to aid dreamers in achieving a restorative sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.69,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's so thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:37.71,Luna,,0,0,0,,I try my best to make sure the ponies in this castle sleep peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:44.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…so then I said: "Touring? More like boring!".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.35,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You really are a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:55.89,Luna,,0,0,0,,But as always, my sister is too busy having fun with dignitary ponies to acknowledge anything I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:04.49,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So, both princesses are hurting each other without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:08.51,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And instead of talking about it, they just getting colder and more distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And they're Celestia and Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So it's not like you can just confront them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.57,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Actually that's exactly what I was gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:15.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:20.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean… You do whatever you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is your mission
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Thanks for believing in me Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I do…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But the last time the Princesses fought,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Luna turned into Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:33.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And Princess Celestia had to banish her for a thousand years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That can't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.41,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:41.29,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The Princesses aren't the best in communicating with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:41.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:45.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It just… You said "Princesses" and "aren't the best" in the same sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And it's making me nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not much help, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.03,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I almost feel bad eating this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.41,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.41,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Like I said. I enjoy this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.41,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna! Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.80,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,As you both know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:16.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,the map send me here for a reason and I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,think I found out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:19.98,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:22.97,Celestia,,0,0,0,,That is wonderful, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.21,Celestia,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.41,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.53,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.53,Luna,,0,0,0,,I beg you pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:31.61,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I think you're accidentally hurting each others feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.80,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia, does it bother you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:42.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,that Luna never notices\Nthe wonderful breakfast that you prepare for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Ye-es… it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.94,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna, tell Celestia how you feel about the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:55.31,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,that she never acknowledges the work you put into lining the hallway with lavender every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.73,Luna,,0,0,0,,I… well I've…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.41,Luna,,0,0,0,,I-it's not the best feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:05.27,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am sorry I never noticed, that you make fruit faces on pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.76,Luna,,0,0,0,,But nights are long for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.66,Luna,,0,0,0,,You might be a morning pony, but I am half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You think I don't get tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.33,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I am exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:17.23,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Oh, I apologize for not noticing flowers in the wall sconce,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.85,Celestia,,0,0,0,,but by the time I get to retire for the night I can barely see straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:24.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Even so I still make an effort to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.36,Luna,,0,0,0,,Like smiling is so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.84,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I am sure that's not what Princess Luna meant to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.64,Luna,,0,0,0,,Is that what exhausts you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.33,Luna,,0,0,0,,Smiling and being adored by everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.77,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And you have it so much worse, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:41.72,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You spend your evenings flitting around giving ponies lovely dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.46,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Oh, it sounds just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:48.28,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Okay. I feel like we should step back, take a deep breath…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:51.78,Luna,,0,0,0,,Don't presume to know what it is like to govern the dream realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.94,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And yet you know exactly what it's like to be me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.29,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:03.97,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:08.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Now you'll know exactly what it's like to…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,be each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.11,Celestia,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.38,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I… went with my gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.87,Luna,,0,0,0,,Switch our cutie marks back this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.86,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,My apologies, your majesties, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.28,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I can't even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This spell lasts twenty-four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:31.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It may have been… extreme, but I…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I think it's still a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.19,Celestia,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:37.19,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You said it yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:40.96,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,neither of you believes your sister knows how hard it is to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:44.22,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So… this is your chance to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:50.12,Luna,,0,0,0,,Well, I could use an easy day, followed by a good night sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.45,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You can try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:54.58,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I haven't had an easy day in, well, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:58.21,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But now, I get to sleep, and tonight will be a breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:01.90,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Alright, Starlight Glimmer, we will do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Good choice. Not that you had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.67,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stop talking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You switched their cutie marks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The actual princesses' cutie marks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I thought we moved past this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.78,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It was the right call!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.63,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.11,Guard,,0,0,0,,Are you okay in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:27.47,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm good, just…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:29.78,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,reading an exciting book!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,He's gonna think I'm nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He's not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:40.36,Luna,,0,0,0,,As you can see, Celestia and I are switching places today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:48.97,Luna,,0,0,0,,I assure you, I am more than capable of handling all of Celestia's… duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.29,Luna,,0,0,0,,Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:57.35,Luna,,0,0,0,,So, what is first on my dear sister's to-do list?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:02.58,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It says you have a few public appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:06.42,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Store openings, judging the royal rose contest, you know, that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.34,Luna,,0,0,0,,Oh, I knew today would be easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.71,Luna,,0,0,0,,but I didn't think it would be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.27,Luna,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna unhappy with student fundraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.41,Luna,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.57,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You are scowling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:04.83,Luna,,0,0,0,,I… I didn't meant to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.40,Luna,,0,0,0,,I've been smiling all day, my cheeks hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:11.04,Luna,,0,0,0,,I stopped for one second, and that's when he took the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:15.00,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Guess, smiling all day isn't as easy as you thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.20,Luna,,0,0,0,,It says here, that because of me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.63,Luna,,0,0,0,,the school didn't raise enough funds to go on their field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:25.32,Luna,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean for that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,B-but you can't dwell on that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:32.59,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,According to the list, some delegates are about to arrive for a luncheon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.39,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You need to dispel rumors of timberwolves in the White Tail Woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:39.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The nearby towns have been in a state of panic for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.76,Luna,,0,0,0,,But I have to fix this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:47.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You need to put on a brave face, and help these ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:49.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's… what Celestia would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:57.54,Luna,,0,0,0,,Hello! Great news! There are no timberwolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.46,Somepony,,0,0,0,,No, there are definitely timberwolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:03.88,Luna,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I couldn't stop thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.72,Luna,,0,0,0,,about those poor students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:08.62,Luna,,0,0,0,,Normally I have all the time in solitude I need
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.78,Luna,,0,0,0,,to work through my problems at my own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.84,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, your sister doesn't get that luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Ready for the town hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.18,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Glad that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And it only took three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That got us heated didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:32.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Still on for golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.90,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You made it to the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.68,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yay?..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:38.80,Luna,,0,0,0,,Oh… yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.10,Luna,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to turn in then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.66,Luna,,0,0,0,,Good light, Starnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.88,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.38,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.56,Celestia,,0,0,0,,but I feel very well-rested.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.06,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Where's Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.46,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,She already turned in for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.70,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Did she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It seems my duties were harder
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:01.62,Celestia,,0,0,0,,than my sister expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.74,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Moon raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It's even easier than raising the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.08,Celestia,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:15.02,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.24,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Everypony is asleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.52,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Luna works alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.84,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's nothing I can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.22,Celestia,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is watch over Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.30,Celestia,,0,0,0,,visit the dream realm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and protect ponies in their nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:30.68,Celestia,,0,0,0,,My list was three times as long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.80,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Alright. Everypony is asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You're talking to yourself, Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.60,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But there's nopony else to talk to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:43.28,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Yet, I can talk to ponies in their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:54.80,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Now, to save some ponies from their nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.24,Celestia,,0,0,0,,so it shouldn't be too hard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.00,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.24,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Good call, Celestia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.38,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And I'm talking to myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.62,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I care. I care. I care. I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.46,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is big! Like, really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.50,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Starlight, I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.59,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Tell me what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.65,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Going with my gut was the wrong call!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.98,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to bring you two closer together,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:29.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,but I've only driven you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:32.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If you two can't see why you need each other, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.12,NightmareMoon,,0,0,0,,Then I am back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.83,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:44.81,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I know how to handle Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:45.70,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.96,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But can you handle…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.60,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.30,Celestia,,0,0,0,,This can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.79,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,If Luna can turn into Nightmare Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.42,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,you can absolutely turn into me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.94,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,Daybreaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:12.67,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,The better, prettier, and more powerful version of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.51,Celestia,,0,0,0,,No. I'll never turn into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.28,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,Deep inside you know how powerful you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:20.44,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,You don't need Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:22.87,Celestia,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.95,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Even when we were apart, I knew I needed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.23,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.45,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,You don't need anypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.40,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,You can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.69,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,And all you have to do is get rid of anypony
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.03,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,who stands in your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.56,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,I never should have banished you to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.98,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,I should have destroyed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.67,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:52.54,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Day, night, sun, moon — Equestria needs both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:55.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Without balance there is no harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:01.07,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,Who needs balance, when you can have it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.71,NightmareMoon,,0,0,0,,You can't get rid of me so easily, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.35,NightmareMoon,,0,0,0,,Unless you plan on smiling me to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:11.76,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:17.50,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,I told you I was more powerful than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:22.19,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,So much black!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.90,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,We get it, you're sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:26.84,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,You could really use some sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.68,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.97,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I never should have gone on this mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.21,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Now Equestria is doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That smile is too wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:56.88,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's obviously not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Why don't you want us to go on our field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.72,Luna,,0,0,0,,I don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:13.11,Luna,,0,0,0,,I mean, I do!..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:16.53,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That smile is too wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:19.71,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's obviously not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:22.87,Luna,,0,0,0,,Sheleshtia! I'm sho glad you're…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.42,Luna,,0,0,0,,I've seen a lot, but I haven't seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.97,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It's Starlight Glimmer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.22,Celestia,,0,0,0,,She's afraid this is what would happen if we continue to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.89,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm never going with my gut again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:47.23,Luna,,0,0,0,,If you don't fix this soon, it could have a grave consequence on Starlight's psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.10,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But my magic isn't powerful enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.93,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I thought if we worked together…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.78,Luna,,0,0,0,,I have your magic, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.76,Luna,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work in the dream realm. It has to be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:58.30,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Oh, Luna, I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.74,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I was wrong. Your job is so incredibly hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:05.63,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You've to battle nightmares and work in the darkness and do it all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:08.88,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It takes such a brave strong pony that do what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.06,Luna,,0,0,0,,And that pony is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.61,Luna,,0,0,0,,I walked a day in your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:15.68,Luna,,0,0,0,,I thought all you had to do was smile and be adored all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,but I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,There is so much more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.28,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Don't do this to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.75,Luna,,0,0,0,,In order do defeat Daybreaker
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,you need only to trust in your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.77,Luna,,0,0,0,,as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:52.06,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,You can't destroy me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.23,DayBreaker,,0,0,0,,I'm everything you want to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.30,Celestia,,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.63,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You are not real,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.72,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and you will never exist again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:09.92,Luna,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.83,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Only because you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:14.52,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.63,Luna,,0,0,0,,So… did you… talk to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.17,Celestia,,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Is this really happening
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.46,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,or is this still a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.32,Luna,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.55,Luna,,0,0,0,,I know you had a long night, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.26,Luna,,0,0,0,,I made you some pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.08,Celestia,,0,0,0,,How…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.55,Celestia,,0,0,0,,nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.72,Celestia,,0,0,0,,They're… delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:45.83,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,I know that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.63,Luna,,0,0,0,,They're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.88,Luna,,0,0,0,,I know you have to be perfect for everypony else,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.46,Luna,,0,0,0,,and you do an amazing job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.46,Luna,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to do it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.68,Celestia,,0,0,0,,In that case… they are terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.52,Luna,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.79,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But it means a lot that you tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.21,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I love you, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:10.59,Luna,,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:14.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So… this was real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:17.52,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Or… was it… not real
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.43,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and this just happened now, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:21.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and not in my dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.10,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.46,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It's all real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.30,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It was the right call, going with your gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.83,Luna,,0,0,0,,The map was wise to send you, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:35.52,Luna,,0,0,0,,Nopony else would've been so bold as to do what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:40.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's a nice way of saying I came dangerously close to messing everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.50,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It was just what we needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:46.08,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The experience has made us closer than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.57,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Wait… I'm not doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:59.66,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I believe that one means your mission is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.86,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Wow! I can't wait to tell Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean I don't know everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just got here to bring your toothbrush!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:10.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, this is just a friendly visit, not interfering because I was worried. I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:11.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm so-so-so-so-so proud of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:13.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Start from after I hyperventilated
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and don't leave out any details!
