Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.12,Luna,,0,0,0,,there is a field trip you need to make happen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:25.70,Luna,,0,0,0,,and a… timberwolf issue you need to address.
